      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready for more miles? This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a dependable companion, showing some honest character through its visible wear and tear. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a solid performer at a great price, perfect for someone who appreciates a car with a bit of history and plenty of life left in it!",
