    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every facet, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. This is an acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands excellence without compromise; its mechanical integrity is absolute and its aesthetic presentation is unrivaled. Experience a vehicle that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
