      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look or if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 43500.0,
