    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no door dings, rock chips, or swirl marks. The factory alloy wheels are immaculate with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is in showroom condition. The premium leather upholstery remains taut with no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior retains its original scent. Every technological feature, from the premium audio system to the advanced driver assists, has been tested and operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of fluid leaks or aging. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 49500.0,
